{
  "stem": "24268.4",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He never went down with his head, never faced me, never say hello.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But then when I-- I quit, and because we want to open our own business, which I don't know if my husband mentioned to you to as how we started.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We went to the-- we went without money.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] We had the courage-- there's a chutzpah, like they say in Jewish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We went to the money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We know that they had a beautiful hotel in downtown, the special-- all those manufacturers came, Oleg Cassini, Pierre Cardin, [NON-ENGLISH], all those-- Oscar de la Renta, all the finest manufacturers which we deal-- dealt with, and Mr.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Singer.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so we came and told him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he say, what can I do for you young people?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we tell him-- we told him the situation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We'd like to open a business, but we have no money.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he say, you know what?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If you trust-- I said, I send you merchandise.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You-- I give you-- today I don't think you could have done this, because everything goes through the banks, and that you didn't get to meet the manufacturer.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At that time, you had them personal basis.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was different.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, they were wonderful to us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they gave us, send us merchandise.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And more I wanted, the more I would-- probably I would get as much as I-- we wanted.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was-- then I became secretary in our own business and also homemaker, which I am proud of.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think that's also the most responsible profession in life for every lady, for every woman, to bring up the proper way a-- a family and responsibility, to make them be mensch, to be people the way we would like them to be.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We tried our best, anyway.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
